works.description: The latest toy to hit the marine leisure market is the new AS-2 Scooter from the house of Aqua Star. Made to give riders a one-of-a-kind scuba experience, the high-tech Aqua Star underwater scooter for two has been built upon the success of the single seat AS1 model. Great for diving enthusiasts, turnkey leisure operators and couples, the AS2 lets you explore underwater wonders with the utmost safety.
